title: Katy Perry Prism Vinyl Wav
description:
Prism is the fourth studio album by American singer-songwriter Katy Perry, released by Capitol Records on October 18, 2013. While the album was initially planned to be "darker" than her previous material, Prism ultimately became a prominently dance-inspired record. The singer worked with several past collaborators, while enlisting new producers and guest vocals. Much of Prism revolves around the themes of living in the present, relationships, and self-empowerment.









Wav format

Recorded using sony soundforge vinyl recording/restoration, peak normalization and restoration.

The album has a dynamic range meter rating of 9-10 instead of the 4-5 you find on the cd version,

Ripped with a music hall 2.2 turntable with the standard cartridge/needle and a phono box s pre amp
